      "message": "I\u0027m still having a bit a hard time figuring out how thisfits in with fansensor in dbus-sensors (since I don\u0027t use it), which also hosts inventory items for fans and can do its own presence detection.  Are the Inventory.Item interfaces it has just unused by anything since there\u0027s no associations?",
